EndTickGroup:
Defines the tick group that this tick function must finish in. These groups determine the relative order of when objects tick during a frame update.

@see ETickingGroup
TickInterval: The frequency in seconds at which this tick function will be executed.  If less than or equal to 0 then it will tick every frame
bTickEvenWhenPaused: Bool indicating that this function should execute even if the game is paused. Pause ticks are very limited in capabilities. *
bStartWithTickEnabled: If true, this tick function will start enabled, but can be disabled later on.
bAllowTickOnDedicatedServer: If we allow this tick to run on a dedicated server
